						</td>
					</tr>
					<tr>
						<td align="left" height="136" valign="top">
						<h1><em>Lord, give me the patience to serve everyone as my own; the wisdom to understand<br />
						others feelings; the knowledge to learn as well as to instruct; the kindness to treat<br />
						everyone equally at all times; the strength to endure long hours and hard work; the<br />
						desire to serve others as I would my own family; the humility to accept words of<br />
						thanks and praise; the Compassion to touch another&#39;s soul; the pride and the right to<br />
						smile when I have served a family well; and, Lord, most importantly the right to shed<br />
						an honest tear when my heart is touched; Lord, make me thankful that I am a<br />
						Funeral Director.</em></h1>
						</td>
